creator: Cara Fitness
descriptionHtml:
Women over 40... It's time to take back your life.
Join the Cara Fitness method and find your mojo.
Lose weight, tone up, lose belly fat & reignite your energy levels!

Cara Fitness Premium Plan monthly or as a 3 month subscription

1. Follow a proven step by step program with the daily plan
2. Set your goals and track your progress
3. Get the real time 15 minute workout library
4. Join the monthly challenges. We go through it together as a team
5. Find your calm with our quick meditations
6. Stretch & flow to give you back your flexibility
7. Midlife Mayhem for all things midlife, perimenopause & menopause.
8. Weight loss & hormone balancing nutrition & recipes
9. Specific courses including Golden Power beginner 10 minute workouts
10. Join the Cara Fitness community and find women just like you!

Cara Fitness Basic monthly
1. Get the real time workout library
2. Set your goals and track your progress
3. Join the Cara Fitness community and find women just like you!

LET'S DO THIS!

"My whole life style has changed since I have joined Cara Fitness. Not to be missed!" - Julie Fryer
"It makes sense & it works!" - Katharine Coleman
"Cara’s energy and enthusiasm is so infectious that my goals come more easily" - Loraine Barry
"There's something magical about that 15 minutes. I feel ALIVE! I trust Cara!" - Susie Leach
"Cara's motivation and dedication is next to none. Thank you Cara!" - Loraine Rath
"Cara is always on hand for questions & advice! I would recommend Cara to anyone - she’s just great!" - Sally Bolingbroke

Download the app for free today!
